# Exception: vendored, pinned AOP-XML schema directory (version-controlled).
# The blanket aop-wiki-xml* rule above matches data/schema/aop-wiki-xml.xsd,
# but the vendored XSD + its provenance pin + the coverage allowlist are
# tracked source artifacts, not transient snapshot downloads. Raw
# data/aop-wiki-xml* snapshot downloads stay ignored by the rule above.
!data/schema/
!data/schema/aop-wiki-xml.xsd
!data/schema/aop-wiki-xml.xsd.SOURCE

